{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Usher syndrome and driving"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/usher-syndrome-and-driving.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/usher-syndrome-and-driving"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"2277","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"Driving with Usher's syndrome","overview":"Usher syndrome is a medical condition you must tell DVLA about","updated_at":"2012-10-02T12:14:38+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> if you have Usher syndrome.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to \u00a31,000 if you don\u2019t tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> about a medical condition that affects your driving. If you\u2019re involved in an accident, you may be prosecuted.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Car or motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form V1 and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065620.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download \u2018V1 - Confidential medical information\u2019 (PDF, 253KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Bus, coach or lorry licence</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in forms V1V and AUD1 and send them to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on each form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065275.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download \u2018V1V - Confidential medical information\u2019 (PDF, 261KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065271.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download \u2018AUD1 - Confidential medical information\u2019 (PDF, 249KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Driving with a disability or a health condition","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/driving%2Fdisability-health-condition.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Information about medical conditions that affect your ability to drive","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=driving%2Fdisability-health-condition","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving/disability-health-condition"},"parent":{"title":"Driving","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/driving.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Book your driving test or get a tax disc online, find out the legal requirements for buying, owning, importing or scrapping a car or motorcycle, and read about your rights and responsibilities as a driver.","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=driving","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving"},"parent":null}}]],["related",[{"title":"Medical conditions, disabilities and driving","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/driving-if-disabled.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/driving-if-disabled","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"786","business_proposition":true}}]]],"parts":null}